{"tid":251694,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[置樂嫲孫食評] 狗也不屌系列","createTime":"2017-05-21T07:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T11:13:23.000Z","uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f48bd50f57c8f9c91f96f53b568ad63ef0628fe3","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/145756_dedb3896b1493dd5212ed0a894f9de9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F145756_dedb3896b1493dd5212ed0a894f9de9b.jpg&h=a2918c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/145704_c0a4d65a2ed65ffb14fdad778c3b4224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F145704_c0a4d65a2ed65ffb14fdad778c3b4224.jpg&h=627dfcaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n$38算係咁下話... ？<br />\n<br />\n不過呢，青瓜太少又無香味，紅蘿蔔絲又少又唔清甜，啲菜完全被忽略無左存在感。可唔可以尊重返啲青瓜？<br />\n<br />\n手撕雞，得兩條，都好食少啲肉less evil嘛⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n至於啲麻辣汁，強度可以再增加50%。 <br />\n<br />\n份量少其實還ok，人到中年都唔洗下下食到飽。香港人又成撚日食剩野... 其實真係唔值得俾飽从飯佢地食。<br />\n<br />\n杯茶就太熱喇，又咁大杯，要個客霸住你個位幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n至於個皮蛋呢啲致癌物質，我鳩點的，夾硬生啪落口，又無事喎⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/150026_4f81bc0c2d64f8ef6356369ab0f8815d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F150026_4f81bc0c2d64f8ef6356369ab0f8815d.jpg&h=4e1ece03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再評營商手法，呀你老味～張菜單就影撚到有咁大份得咁大份，有咁靚得咁靚。<br />\n<br />\n明明菜單有6塊皮蛋，你老母上到來得3塊，雖然我唔鐘意食姐，但你都唔好欺騙顧客感情呀？<br />\n<br />\n「岩唔岩呀，呀哥！」<br />\n<br />\n然後果碗撈麵，唉有圖你地自己睇。廢事搞大件事呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後啦，以為自己好撚醒咁係左下角，用細過粒米且仲要俾封邊鐵遮撚住一大半既字寫住「圖片只供參考」。<br />\n<br />\n羞唔羞恥呀你？你咪撚侮辱只供呢兩個字啦，「子宮」係人類起源來嫁！<br />\n<br />\nBtw有無商品說明條例的專家係到？<br />\n<br />\n#頭也不回 #狗也不屌"},{"pid":"004f0476015d40e1db3bb0c77915b36023124904","tid":251694,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"睇黎樓豬好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f69e60673bee8f157983fc2b33d6bce6b4dedb6","tid":251694,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"又一問川館"},{"pid":"c3535b922fdfa21f53303aac413c974ad5fc164f","tid":251694,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"咩黎架 餸定小食"},{"pid":"2bdbeed841be1362b24d004ca6d493e27e40abf5","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎樓豬好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫此文章時，我脫下M屬性香港人的靈魂。<br />\n換上文天詳的心境，直斥其非。<br />\n無非都係無聊無屎柯搵野做姐～"},{"pid":"f74780cfd7c0760ccdb41eed9b469d46baf3029c","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩黎架 餸定小食</blockquote><br />\n撈麵主食，皮蛋小食"},{"pid":"9388ed211f3b182953ecd174454637b0bf9c528d","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又一問川館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n川館無所謂<br />\n問題係啲香港人（唔知老細係咪大陸人）不思進取<br />\n有形無實，鐘意起空中樓閣，基本功唔撚扎實，一味追求包裝，裝修到間鋪鬼死咁靚.....<br />\n<br />\n算喇，人地搵到食開到分店姐係有錢賺，有錢賺就係成功的商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d6cadaea41a83d68d31f3afe0faf9a63816d95","tid":251694,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又一問川館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n川館無所謂<br />\n問題係啲香港人（唔知老細係咪大陸人）不思進取<br />\n有形無實，鐘意起空中樓閣，基本功唔撚扎實，一味追求包裝，裝修到間鋪鬼死咁靚.....<br />\n<br />\n算喇，人地搵到食開到分店姐係有錢賺，有錢賺就係成功的商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d川菜店好鬼<br />\n見過d日日小貓幾隻都唔洗汁"},{"pid":"297ed9b1109bbc6edab26d7cfca8e0046f789c42","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又一問川館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n川館無所謂<br />\n問題係啲香港人（唔知老細係咪大陸人）不思進取<br />\n有形無實，鐘意起空中樓閣，基本功唔撚扎實，一味追求包裝，裝修到間鋪鬼死咁靚.....<br />\n<br />\n算喇，人地搵到食開到分店姐係有錢賺，有錢賺就係成功的商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d川菜店好鬼<br />\n見過d日日小貓幾隻都唔洗汁</blockquote><br />\n唔通支那人來香港洗__錢又會俾我地知咩？"},{"pid":"19b90a26fb804dd3bb4ea667d38979c7a74ee4f4","tid":251694,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇黎樓豬好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫此文章時，我脫下M屬性香港人的靈魂。<br />\n換上文天詳的心境，直斥其非。<br />\n無非都係無聊無屎柯搵野做姐～</blockquote><br />\n俾我都要火既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾40蚊同食屎一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d70b8a99964e677afc34ea7cbb6dc6dd6d46bf","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇黎樓豬好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫此文章時，我脫下M屬性香港人的靈魂。<br />\n換上文天詳的心境，直斥其非。<br />\n無非都係無聊無屎柯搵野做姐～</blockquote><br />\n俾我都要火既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾40蚊同食屎一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我對食無乜要求，碗野入口其實唔太差。<br />\n但做人唔可以咁低賤！草向上生，咁人都要望高處，反思自身的周遭。"},{"pid":"af0a7b45f595186347c0da8d147b504a22b83988","tid":251694,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"張相影得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc08aadd2411decd39d371e3eceb595000d3e5f3","tid":251694,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f2209e578fdae1ba1ea75a5a9fdd63f7c0fb7a","tid":251694,"uid":52525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"On9 張相明明都係皮蛋一碟三件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dba7afb86fa05c88605a0710969e9da08ec16b","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9 張相明明都係皮蛋一碟三件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴孖筋, 又自稱係 講事實啫, 大家評下理喇...."},{"pid":"060e7cf7a44bb2a4160eadaf564c99c38326df47","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>On9 張相明明都係皮蛋一碟三件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴孖筋, 又自稱係 講事實啫, 大家評下理喇....</blockquote>"},{"pid":"895fde708319c3fe2afbd3a0d12bc3bc6d1b4b37","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張相影得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks 呢啲咪叫曲線宣傳囉~"},{"pid":"a772426af5cfaa9210e9ce4bcc83d7e5bc3c814f","tid":251694,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間野其實唔係太差, 我咀賤, 你地親身去評下理~"}]}